headline: OpenAI Insurance Apps Test Arthur J. Gallagher’s Brokerage Model And Fees
summary: OpenAI has launched insurance-native AI tools that let customers compare and purchase policies directly. These applications target complex policy matching and buying, which sits at the core of Arthur J. Gallagher's brokerage role. The development raises the risk of brokers being cut out of the transaction process, putting high commission revenue under pressure. For Arthur J.
